{"body": "@pnegri you don't need to use it. You can use plain ruby methods to archive the same behavior. `composed_of` is only a poor wrapper to give you:\n\n```ruby\ndef price\n  @price ||= Money.new(value, currency)\nend\n\ndef price=(price)\n  @price = price\n\n  self[:value] = price.value\n  self[:currency] = price.currency\nend\n```\n\nOne of the solutions for these issues is stop to use `composed_of`.\n\nRight now this feature is not often used. We have to take into account the trade-off between value and maintainability cost, and the value of this feature is dubious since you can reproduce it easily.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6373918", "created_at": "2012-06-16T15:18:41Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6743#issuecomment-6373918", "updated_at": "2012-06-16T15:27:21Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6743, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e2d0bbd354364b900e156"